Astique â€“ Child Safety Standards

Astique has a zero-tolerance policy towards child sexual abuse and exploitation (CSAE) and any child sexual abuse material (CSAM). We are committed to providing a safe platform for all users.

1. Prohibited Content
Any content involving minors in sexual, exploitative, or harmful situations is strictly forbidden. Users who create, share, or promote such content will be permanently banned.

2. Reporting & Moderation
Users can report unsafe behaviour or content through in-app reporting features or by contacting us at:
support@astique.co

Reported content is reviewed and removed where necessary.

3. Cooperation With Authorities
Astique complies with applicable child safety laws and will cooperate with regional and national law-enforcement agencies when required.

4. Account Actions
We may suspend or terminate accounts that violate our child safety policies without prior notice.

5. Age Requirements
Astique is intended only for users who meet the minimum legal age requirements in their region.

6. Safety Commitment
We continuously improve moderation systems and safety practices to prevent misuse of the platform.
